                     <title xml:lang="he-Latn-x-lc">Me᾿ir ῾ene ῾avarim</title>
                     
                     
                     
                     <title xml:lang="he">מאיר עיני עברים</title>
                     
                     
                     
                     <note>
                        
                        
                        
                        <p>A treatise on Jewish calendar, with comparative tables of the Jewish and Christian eras from <date calendar="Hebrew">5343-6000</date> (i.e. <date calendar="Gregorian">1583-2240</date>), partly in Yiddish. </p>
                        
                        
                        
                        <p>The work is divided into three parts; the current volume contains an introduction and part 1, Shenot olam (folio 14r), i.e. the comparative calendrical tables.</p>
                        
                        
                        
                        <p>Folio 12v contains rhymed pieces in praise of the treatise, by Mordekhai Rokh. </p>
                     
                     
                     
                     </note>
                     
                     
                     
                     <filiation>Uniform with Or 4686. </filiation>
                  
                  
                  
                  </msItem>
               
               
               
               </msContents>
               
               
               
